        "action": "Give solar panels on residential properties legally protected rights to light",
        "additional_details": "1. Extending right to light legislation to include solar panels.\r\n2. Adding caveats to 'Permitted Development' laws to protect solar panels.\r\n3. Ensuring Party Wall Agreements don't affect rights to light of solar panels.\r\n\r\nAt present I believe the Government's 'GREEN' policies are contradictory They are not fit for purpose because different policies can work against its commitment to carbon emission reduction targets.",
